{"tid":1168322,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"計我話坐電動輪椅嘅都唔可以計行動不便","createTime":"2019-05-23T14:57:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-23T15:13:33.000Z","uid":24390,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f5eafca1aff706acbc3c22ead22db5b5aceb0626","tid":1168322,"uid":24390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T14:57:34.000Z","msg":"話說屋企附近唔知點解有好多電動輪椅車手<br />\n成日都係行人路上面風馳電制<br />\n又冇得硬cut佢地<br />\n如果唔係隻腳就係咁先<br />\n搭𨋢又畀佢地霸曬啲位<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最激氣係試過有兩個車手係運動場霸咗兩條線慢駛<br />\n明明人地跑步係練cardio,佢地就唔知有咩目的<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n計我話電椅車手唔可以當傷殘<br />\n佢地搭車一定要收triple錢<br />\n認同請分享<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e76e5c32e44682f618b1d4bbde5957536a8e3ce5","tid":1168322,"uid":24390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T15:13:33.000Z","msg":"推"}]}